Personal Notes: The main game is pretty short, (perhaps around 10 hours) but the achievements are very grindy. Spent most of my time getting 3 stars on the challenge maps, some of which were very frustrating at times. I unnecessarily spent a few extra hours on one of the challenge maps as Robin. Definitely could have done some maps quicker, but beware for achievement hunters, this game will take you a decent chunk of time regardless. At least 80 hours.
